* text=auto eol=lf
# Shell scripts executed under WSL MUST stay LF: a CRLF `set -euo pipefail\r`
# makes WSL bash abort with "set: pipefail: invalid option name", which silently
# broke the verthor vertical-reframe path in v1.4 (shorts never generated).
# `* text=auto eol=lf` already implies this; this explicit rule documents the
# hard requirement and survives edits to the wildcard line.
*.sh text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mov binary
*.mkv binary
*.webm binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.onnx binary
*.gguf binary
*.bin binary
*.pdf binary
